# Implementation Plan - Agent Hub New Pages

This plan covers the implementation of the `/templates` and `/workspace` pages, which are currently empty in the Agent Hub project.

## Proposed Changes

### [Component Name]

#### [NEW] [templates/page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/LUKAS.WIDMER/Downloads/Claude%20code/agent-hub/src/app/templates/page.tsx)
- Create a grid layout using `AgentGrid`.
- Fetch (or mock) a list of [Template](file:///c:/Users/LUKAS.WIDMER/Downloads/Claude%20code/agent-hub/src/types/index.ts#92-100) objects from [src/types/index.ts](file:///c:/Users/LUKAS.WIDMER/Downloads/Claude%20code/agent-hub/src/types/index.ts).
- Include a search bar and category filters (Development, Marketing, etc.).
- Add a "Use Template" action to each card.

#### [NEW] [workspace/page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/LUKAS.WIDMER/Downloads/Claude%20code/agent-hub/src/app/workspace/page.tsx)
- Implement a chat-like interface.
- Left sidebar: List of recently used agents or active conversations.
- Main area: Scrollable message list using the [Message](file:///c:/Users/LUKAS.WIDMER/Downloads/Claude%20code/agent-hub/src/types/index.ts#84-91) type.
- Bottom: Text input for sending messages with a "Send" button.
- Integrate [AgentAvatar](file:///c:/Users/LUKAS.WIDMER/Downloads/Claude%20code/agent-hub/src/types/index.ts#36-42) for the active assistant.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- No existing test suite found. We will focus on manual verification of the UI.

### Manual Verification
1. Navigate to `/templates` and verify:
   - The grid of templates loads correctly.
   - Search and filtering by category work as expected.
   - The "Use Template" button is visible and interactive.
2. Navigate to `/workspace` and verify:
   - The chat layout is responsive and correctly aligned.
   - Messages can be "sent" (added to the local state).
   - The agent avatar is displayed and animates correctly.
   - Switching between agents in the sidebar (if implemented) updates the chat context.
